flowchart LR
    I1[Image: dog on beach] --> IE[Image encoder]
    T1[Text: dog on beach] --> TE[Text encoder]
    IE --> IV[Image embedding]
    TE --> TV[Text embedding]
    IV --> S[Similarity matrix]
    TV --> S
    S --> P[Pull matching pairs together]
    S --> N[Push mismatched pairs apart]
